{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "product_development", "channel": "vehicle_delivery", "user": "jane_smith", "message": "Hey team, don't forget our weekly meeting tomorrow at 10 AM to discuss the progress of the new model development. Please prepare your updates!", "created_at": 1620500000000}}
{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "supply_chain", "channel": "supply_disruptions", "user": "john_doe", "message": "Hi All, could you please share the updated list of suppliers for the battery components? We need to finalize our budget allocation for the next quarter.", "created_at": 1620600000000}}
{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "product_development", "channel": "vehicle_delivery", "user": "amanda_foster", "message": "Jane, I've received some customer feedback regarding the user interface of our latest model. I think we should discuss this in tomorrow's meeting.", "created_at": 1620700000000}}
{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "supply_chain", "channel": "supply_disruptions", "user": "amanda_foster", "message": "John, I've completed the QA process for the current supplier list. We are good to proceed with the finalized ones.", "created_at": 1620800000000}}
{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "product_development", "channel": "vehicle_delivery", "user": "jane_smith", "message": "Amanda, that's great! Please include the feedback in your report for tomorrow's meeting. It's important we catch these issues early.", "created_at": 1620900000000}}
{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "supply_chain", "channel": "supply_disruptions", "user": "john_doe", "message": "Hello team, I've just finished analyzing the 2025 supply chain data. Unfortunately, we had more disruptions than anticipated. These disruptions significantly impacted our vehicle delivery schedule.", "create_at": 1620500000000}}
{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "supply_chain", "channel": "supply_disruptions", "user": "john_doe", "message": "To be precise, 18% of our vehicle deliveries experienced delays due to these supply chain constraints. This is a significant figure and we need to work on strategies to mitigate such issues in the future.", "create_at": 1620500000500}}
{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "supply_chain", "channel": "supply_disruptions", "user": "amanda_foster", "message": "Thank you for sharing this, John. It's clear that these supply chain issues are having a major impact on our production. Let's discuss potential solutions in our next meeting.", "create_at": 1620500001000}}
{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "product_development", "channel": "vehicle_delivery", "user": "jane_smith", "message": "It's unfortunate to hear about the supply chain disruptions causing an 18% delay in our vehicle deliveries. We need to communicate this to our customers and assure them we're working on better solutions.", "create_at": 1620500001500}}
